            <div style="font-size:16px;">Released: [Feb 2024]</div>
            <p class="title1">1. 1. Special Notice</p>
            <p class="">1.1</p>
            <p class="content">The operator of Sealincloud agrees to provide Sealincloud services to users in accordance with the provisions of this agreement and the operating rules it publishes from time to time. To obtain Sealincloud services, the user of Sealincloud services (hereinafter referred to as "user") must acknowledge and agree to all terms of this agreement (especially the terms that prompt the user to pay attention in bold) and complete all registration procedures as prompted on the page. The user's clicking of the "agree" button during the registration process (or actual use of Sealincloud services) indicates that the user fully accepts this service agreement. If the user has any objections to this service agreement or any part of it, he/she should terminate the registration process (or stop using Sealincloud services). Once you fill in the information as prompted on the registration page, read and agree to this agreement, complete all registration procedures, or use Sealincloud platform services in other ways allowed by Sealincloud, you are bound by this agreement.</p>
            <p class="">1.2</p>
            <p class="content">1.2.1  You confirm that when you complete the registration process or use Sealincloud platform services in other ways allowed by Sealincloud, you should be a natural person (a minor over sixteen years old, whose main source of living is his/her own labor income, is considered a person with full civil capacity), a legal person or other organization with corresponding civil capacity. If you do not have the above-mentioned subject qualification, you and your parents or legal guardians (hereinafter collectively referred to as "guardians") should bear all consequences caused by this, and Sealincloud has the right to cancel your account and claim compensation from you and your guardians. </p>
            <p class="content">1.2.2 Sealincloud attaches great importance to the protection of the safety of the collection and use of personal information of teenagers. Sealincloud suggests that any minor under the age of 18 participating in online activities should obtain the verifiable consent of his/her guardian in advance and abide by the "National Convention on Internet Civilization for Teenagers". Guardians should bear the primary responsibility for the risk of minors' online activities and the protection of minors' relevant online privacy.</p>
            <p class="">1.3</p>
            <p class="content">
            After the user successfully registers, the operator of Sealincloud will provide Sealincloud services to the user based on the objective needs of using Sealincloud services when applying for and registering for Sealincloud services, according to the registration requirements. Users have the right to use Sealincloud services on the basis of Sealincloud operator's opening and agreeing to provide services to them. At the same time, the user agrees:
            </p>
            <p class="content">1.3.1  The user should properly keep the Sealincloud account and password.</p>
            <p class="content">1.3.2  Without the consent of the operator of Sealincloud, the user shall not sell, transfer, or rent any Sealincloud account or Sealincloud nickname without authorization. </p>
            <p class="content">1.3.3  During the use of Sealincloud services, the user must be responsible for his/her own behavior in using Sealincloud services, for any information published or made public by the user through Sealincloud services, and for any consequences arising therefrom. </p>
            <p class="content">1.3.4  Users can confirm and control the public way and visible range of the information they submit, publish or display in the process of using Sealincloud services through the setting function.</p>
            <p class="">1.4</p>
            <p class="content">During the use of Sealincloud services, the user has legal rights and bears corresponding legal responsibilities for his/her own behavior in using Sealincloud services and for any information published or made public through Sealincloud services. At the same time, the user agrees: </p>
            <p class="content">1.4.1  The operator of Sealincloud has a non-exclusive and non-transferable right to use the content of Sealincloud (the content of Sealincloud refers to the information already published by the user on Sealincloud, including but not limited to text, pictures, videos, audio, etc.) during the contract period.</p>
            <p class="content">1.4.2  Without the prior written permission of the operator of Sealincloud, the user shall not illegally capture the content of Sealincloud by himself/herself or authorize or assist any third party. "Illegal capture" refers to the behavior of obtaining content data by using programs or non-normal browsing techniques.</p>
            <p class="">1.5</p>
            <p class="content">Users should strictly abide by the Robots agreement published by the operator of Sealincloud when using Sealincloud services. Without the prior written consent of the operator of Sealincloud, no user shall visit Sealincloud platform or collect any content of Sealincloud in violation of the above provisions in any way by himself/herself or entrust any third party.</p>
            <p class="">1.6</p>
            <p class="content">Within the scope permitted by law, the user agrees and authorizes the operator of Sealincloud to take any form of legal action, including but not limited to complaints, lawsuits and other necessary rights protection measures against the behavior that infringes the user's legitimate rights (including but not limited to unauthorized copying, use, editing, plagiarism, etc.).</p>
            <p class="">1.7</p>
            <p class="content">The operator of Sealincloud has the right to directly entrust its affiliated companies or other third-party companies to operate, manage and perform the rights and obligations under this service or this agreement without obtaining additional authorization from the user. The operator of Sealincloud will try to avoid the inconvenience caused to the user by the above-mentioned entrustment or change in the use of Sealincloud services, and will try to notify the user in a timely manner through the website, platform, private message, email, etc. In this agreement, an affiliated company refers to any enterprise that controls a party, is controlled by a party, or is jointly controlled by the same entity with a party. Control refers to directly or indirectly owning more than fifty percent (50%) of the equity, voting rights or management rights of the enterprise.</p>
            <p class="">1.8</p>
            <p class="content">In order to improve the user's experience and satisfaction with the use of Sealincloud services, the user agrees that the operator of Sealincloud can conduct research and analysis on user data to further optimize Sealincloud services.</p>
            <p class="">1.9</p>
            <p class="content">1.9.1  Sealincloud has the right to formulate and modify this agreement and/or various rules from time to time according to the update of national laws and regulations and the adjustment of product and service rules, and to publicize them in advance in the form of website publicity. If you continue to use Sealincloud platform services, it means that you accept the revised agreement and rules. In case of any dispute, the latest relevant agreement and rules of Sealincloud shall prevail. </p>
            <p class="content">1.9.2  And when you use a specific service of Sealincloud, the service may have a separate agreement, relevant business rules, etc. (hereinafter referred to as "rules"). All rules that Sealincloud has published or may publish in the future are an integral part of this agreement and have the same legal effect as this agreement. Unless otherwise expressly stated, any services provided by Sealincloud and its affiliated companies (hereinafter referred to as "Sealincloud platform services") are subject to this agreement. You promise to accept and abide by the provisions of this agreement. If you disagree with the provisions of this agreement, you should immediately stop the registration process or stop using Sealincloud platform services; if you continue to visit and use Sealincloud platform services, it is deemed that you have been aware of and fully agree to all the contents of this agreement.</p>
            <br/>
            <p class="title1">2.  Service Content</p>
            <p class="">2.1</p>
            <p class="content">The specific content of Sealincloud services is provided by the operator of Sealincloud according to the actual situation, including but not limited to users using Sealincloud services to publish views, comments, pictures, videos, forward links, etc. The operator of Sealincloud has the right to upgrade or adjust the form of its services or products and will update the page to inform users in time.</p>
            <p class="">2.2</p>
            <p class="content">The user understands that the operator of Sealincloud only provides technical services related to Sealincloud services. Besides, the equipment related to the relevant network services (such as personal computers, mobile phones, and other devices related to accessing the Internet or mobile network) and the required fees (such as telephone fees and Internet fees paid for accessing the Internet, and mobile phone fees paid for using the mobile network) are all borne by the user.</p>
            <p class="title1">3.  Service Changes, Interruptions, or Terminations</p>
            <p class="">3.1</p>
            <p class="content">Given the unique nature of online services (including but not limited to server stability issues, malicious network attacks, etc., and other situations that Sealincloud operator cannot control), users agree that Sealincloud operator has the right to interrupt or terminate part or all of Sealincloud services at any time. In such cases, the Sealincloud operator will try to notify affected users as soon as possible through webpage announcements, system notifications, private messages, SMS reminders, or other reasonable methods.</p>
            <p class="">3.2</p>
            <p class="content">Users understand that Sealincloud operator needs to inspect or maintain the service platform (such as internet websites, applications, etc.) or related equipment regularly or irregularly. If such situations cause a reasonable interruption of service, Sealincloud operator is not responsible, but will try to give advance notice as much as possible.</p>
            <p class="">3.3</p>
            <p class="content">If any of the following situations occur, Sealincloud operator has the right to interrupt or terminate Sealincloud services provided under this agreement to the user at any time without any liability to the user or any third party. The user shall bear all losses caused by this: </p>
            <p class="content">3.3.1 The personal information provided by the user is not true; </p>
            <p class="content">3.3.2 The user violates laws, regulations, national policies, or usage rules stipulated in this agreement;</p>
            <p class="content">3.3.3 The user does not pay the relevant service fees as stipulated when using paid services;</p>
            <p class="content">3.3.4 The user intentionally or unintentionally infringes on the rights and interests of individuals, enterprises, and social groups, including but not limited to patent rights, copyrights, trademark rights, or name rights, reputation rights, honor rights, portrait rights, privacy rights, etc;</p>
            <p class="content">3.3.5 The user damages the image of regulatory departments, state organs, and the government;</p>
            <p class="content">3.3.6 The user damages the goodwill or reputation of Sealincloud operator and its affiliated companies in any way; </p>
            <p class="content">3.3.7 Sealincloud operator has other reasonable reasons to believe that it is necessary to interrupt or terminate the provision of Sealincloud services to the user.</p>
            <p class="">3.4</p>
            <p class="content">Sealincloud is constantly changing and improving its services. Leopard Cloud may add or delete features, or temporarily or completely stop a service. Users agree that Leopard Cloud has the right to exercise these rights and does not need to bear any responsibility to users or third parties.</p>

            <p class="title1">4.  Usage Rules</p>
            <p class="">4.1</p>
            <p class="content">Users can edit their account name, nickname, avatar, and introduction in their registration information (hereinafter referred to as "account information"), but they must comply with relevant laws and regulations and should not contain illegal and bad information. Users should use their real identity information and personal information when using Sealincloud account to create, publish, and disseminate information content. They should not register with false or impersonated resident identity information or corporate-related information. If there are any changes to the user's personal data, the user should update it in a timely manner. Without the authorization of the relevant right holder, the user shall not register Sealincloud account in the name of others or other organizations, nor shall they use misleading information to register Sealincloud account, including but not limited to names, avatars, or introductions that mislead people into believing that the account is associated with other individuals or organizations. During the process of editing the registration information, the user shall not publish any information that violates the laws and regulations of the People's Republic of China and goes against social morality.</p>
            <p class="">4.2</p>
            <p class="content"> Sealincloud operator will continuously improve and implement user information security management systems and technical security control measures. Sealincloud operator will protect the user's privacy content involved in the use of Sealincloud services. For Sealincloud content that users post or store in Sealincloud, Sealincloud operator suggests that users back up regularly. Users understand and agree that if users stop using Sealincloud services by using the account cancellation function or if Sealincloud service is terminated or canceled, Sealincloud operator cannot return or provide any data to users.</p>
            <p class="">4.3</p>
            <p class="content">Since the premise of the existence of Sealincloud services is the account provided by the user during the process of applying to open Sealincloud services, the user should not transfer or lend their account or password to others. If the user finds that their account or Sealincloud service is used illegally by others, they should immediately notify the Sealincloud operator. If the account, password, and Sealincloud service are used illegally by others due to hacking behaviors or the user's negligence in custody, the user shall bear the relevant responsibility.</p>
            <p class="">4.4</p>
            <p class="content">Users should speak civilly in the process of using Leopard Cloud services and respect other users' personal rights and identity rights according to law, to jointly establish a harmonious, civilized, and polite online social environment.</p>
            <p class="">4.5</p>
            <p class="content">In the process of using Sealincloud services, users must follow the following principles: </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.1 Do not violate the laws and regulations of the People's Republic of China and related international treaties or rules; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.2 Do not violate the network protocols, regulations, procedures, and industry rules related to network services and Leopard Cloud services; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.3 Do not engage in any behavior that may adversely affect the normal operation of the internet or mobile network; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.4 Do not upload, display, or disseminate any false, impersonating, harassing, defamatory, aggressive, abusive, intimidating, racially discriminatory, libelous, privacy-invading, pornographic, obscene, maliciously plagiarized, violent, bloody, suicidal, self-harming, or any other illegal information or materials;</p>
            <p class="content">4.5.5 Do not infringe on the legal rights and interests of any individual, enterprise, public institution, or social group, including but not limited to patent rights, copyrights, trademark rights, or name rights, reputation rights, honor rights, portrait rights, privacy rights, etc; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.6 Do not damage the image of national organs and the government in any way; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.7 Do not damage the goodwill or reputation of the Sealincloud operator and its affiliated companies in any way; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.8 Do not engage in any other behavior that affects the normal operation of the Sealincloud operator, disrupts the Sealincloud business model, or is harmful to Sealincloud ecosystem; </p>
            <p class="content">4.5.9 Do not use Sealincloud services for any other illegal purposes.</p>
            <p class="">4.6</p>
            <p class="content">For the usage rules and instructions of some specific Sealincloud services, any statements, notifications, warnings, etc., made by the Sealincloud operator through various methods (including but not limited to webpage announcements, system notifications, private messages, SMS reminders, etc.) are considered part of this agreement. If users use such Sealincloud services, it is deemed that the user agrees to the content of these statements, notifications, warnings, etc.</p>
            <p class="">4.7</p>
            <p class="content">Sealincloud operator has the right to review, supervise, and deal with the user's behavior and information in using Sealincloud services, including but not limited to user information (account information, personal information, etc.), published content (location, text, pictures, audio, video, trademarks, patents, publications, etc.), user behavior (building relationships, comments, private messages, information publishing, reporting complaints, etc.).</p>
            <p class="">4.8</p>
            <p class="content">If users find that other users upload illegal and infringing content during the use of Sealincloud services, users can directly click the "report button" to report, and relevant personnel will verify and deal with it as soon as possible. If it involves the handling of personal rights disputes such as name rights, reputation rights, honor rights, portrait rights, privacy rights, etc., users can handle it according to relevant laws and regulations. If the user believes that the above methods cannot solve the problems encountered, or the user feels the need to seek help from judicial administrative organs, the user can report to the relevant organs as soon as possible, and Sealincloud operator will cooperate with the investigation and evidence collection work of the judicial organs according to law.</p>
            <p class="">4.9</p>
            <p class="content">In the process of using Sealincloud services on the Sealincloud platform, you promise to abide by the following agreements: </p>
            <p class="content">4.9.1  All actions taken during the use of Sealincloud platform services comply with the provisions and requirements of national laws, regulations, and other normative documents and various rules of the Sealincloud platform, do not violate the public interest or public morals, do not harm the legal rights of others, and do not violate this agreement and related rules. If you violate the above promise, and any legal consequences arise, you should bear all legal responsibilities in your own name and ensure that Sealincloud is exempt from any loss or additional costs caused by this. </p>
            <p class="content">4.9.2  Do not post information prohibited by the state (unless you obtain legal and sufficient permissions), do not post information suspected of infringing on others' intellectual property rights or other legal rights, do not post information that violates the public interest or public morals, public order and good customs, do not post other information suspected of being illegal or violating this agreement and various rules.</p>
            <p class="content">4.9.3   Prohibition of commercialization of services. The user promises that without the consent of Sealincloud, the user cannot use Sealincloud's services for sales or other commercial purposes. If the user needs to use the service for commercial purposes, they should notify Sealincloud in writing and obtain the explicit authorization of Sealincloud.</p>
            <p class="content">4.9.4 You shall not use any device, software or routine to interfere or attempt to interfere with the normal operation of the Sealincloud platform or any activity being conducted on the Sealincloud platform. You shall not take any action that will impose an unreasonable or disproportionately large load on the network equipment of the Sealincloud platform.</p>
            <p class="">4.10</p>
            <p class="content">You understand and agree that:</p>
            <p class="content">4.10.1   If you violate the above commitments, Sealincloud has the right to take appropriate action or terminate the provision of services to you in accordance with this agreement, without your consent or prior notice to you.</p>
            <p class="content">4.10.2  Based on the designation of relevant laws or the judgment of Sealincloud's service rules, if your behavior is suspected of violating the provisions of laws and regulations or violating the terms of this agreement and/or rules, Sealincloud has the right to take appropriate measures, including but not limited to blocking, deleting infringing information, reducing your credit value or directly stopping the provision of services. If this causes Sealincloud to suffer losses, or be claimed by any third party, or be punished by any administrative authority, you shall compensate Sealincloud for the losses caused and/or expenses incurred, including reasonable attorney's fees.</p>
            <p class="content">4.10.3  For your actions on the Sealincloud platform, including actions not taken on the Sealincloud platform but have affected the Sealincloud platform and its users, Sealincloud has the right to unilaterally determine the nature of your actions and whether they constitute a violation of this agreement and/or rules, and take corresponding measures accordingly. You should keep all evidence related to your behavior and bear the adverse consequences of not being able to provide sufficient evidence.</p>
            <p class="content">4.10.4  For any damage caused to any third party by your alleged breach of commitment, you shall bear all legal responsibilities independently in your own name and ensure that Sealincloud is exempt from the losses or additional costs caused by this.</p>
            <p class="title1">5.  Intellectual Property</p>
            <p class="">5.1</p>
            <p class="content">The "Sealincloud" and related English trademarks "Sealincloud", "Baoliaoyun" and the Sealincloud cartoon graphics are trademarks of the company where Sealincloud is located and its affiliated companies, protected by law, and no one may use them without authorization. Anyone who infringes the copyright and other intellectual property rights of the company, Sealincloud will pursue its legal responsibility according to law.</p>
            <p class="">5.2</p>
            <p class="content">5.2.1. The information (including but not limited to codes, text, charts, logos, button icons, images, sound file clips, digital downloads, data editing, and software) published on the Sealincloud platform is the property of Sealincloud or its content providers and is protected by Chinese and international copyright laws. The compilation of all content on this platform is the exclusive property of Sealincloud, protected by Chinese and international copyright laws. All software on this platform is the property of Sealincloud or its affiliated companies or its software suppliers, protected by Chinese and international copyright laws. Users or third parties must publish, copy, reprint, modify, quote, link, download or use in other ways within the scope authorized by Sealincloud.</p>
            <p class="content">5.2.2. The Sealincloud service platform will strive to maintain its security and convenience for all Sealincloud services, but it does not assume any responsibility for the deletion or storage failure of information (including but not limited to user-posted information) in the service.</p>
            <p class="">5.3</p>
            <p class="content">Sealincloud respects intellectual property and pays attention to protecting the various rights enjoyed by users. In the services contained in Sealincloud, users may need to provide content to Sealincloud through various ways such as uploading and publishing. In this case, the user still enjoys the complete intellectual property rights of such content. When providing content, the user will grant Sealincloud a global, free license, allowing Sealincloud to use, disseminate, copy, modify, re-license, translate, create derivative works, publish, perform and display such content.</p>
            <p class="">5.4</p>
            <p class="content">The information or content posted by users on the Sealincloud platform does not represent the opinions and views of Sealincloud, nor does it mean that Sealincloud agrees with its views or confirms the authenticity of its content. Sealincloud reserves the right to delete any information or content on the website that does not comply with the law or the provisions of this agreement, and reserves the right not to notify users. Sealincloud has the right to delete any information or content on the website that does not comply with the law or the provisions of this agreement, and Sealincloud will try but has no obligation to notify users of the relevant deletion behavior.</p>
            <p class="">5.5</p>
            <p class="content">The information, text, pictures and other materials posted by users on the Sealincloud platform are provided by Sealincloud users, and their authenticity, accuracy and legality are the responsibility of the information publisher. Sealincloud does not provide any guarantee and does not assume any legal responsibility. If the above materials infringe the intellectual property rights or other rights of a third party, the responsibility is borne by the information publisher himself, and Sealincloud does not assume responsibility for this.</p>
            <p class="">5.6</p>
            <p class="content">For disputes caused by improper citation of Sealincloud website content or any loss caused by disputes, Sealincloud does not assume relevant legal responsibility. For users who do not comply with this statement or other illegal and malicious use of Sealincloud website content, Sealincloud reserves the right to pursue its legal responsibility.</p>
            <p class="">5.7</p>
            <p class="content">The copyright and its modification right, update right and interpretation right within the scope permitted by law of the relevant statement of the Sealincloud platform belong to Sealincloud.</p>
            <p class="title1">6.  Privacy Policy</p>
            <p class="">6.1</p>
            <p class="content">6.1.1  Sealincloud will publish and revise the privacy terms from time to time on the Sealincloud platform, and the privacy terms constitute an effective part of this agreement.</p>
            <p class="content">6.1.2. You acknowledge and promise to comply with the "Sealincloud Privacy Terms" during the use of Sealincloud's services. Sealincloud will collect, store, use, disclose and protect your personal information in accordance with the "Sealincloud Privacy Terms" published online. Please read these privacy terms in full to help you better protect your personal information.</p>
            <p class="title1">7.  Disclaimer</p>
            <p class="">7.1</p>
            <p class="content">7.1.1  Sealincloud is responsible for providing you with Sealincloud platform services. However, Sealincloud does not make any express or implied warranty for the Sealincloud platform service, including but not limited to the applicability, error-free or omission, continuity, accuracy, reliability, suitability for a particular purpose of Sealincloud platform service. At the same time, Sealincloud does not make any commitment or guarantee for the validity, accuracy, correctness, reliability, stability, completeness and timeliness of the technology and information involved in the Sealincloud platform service.</p>
            <p class="content">7.1.2  Sealincloud only provides you with Sealincloud platform service, you understand that the information on the Sealincloud platform is published by users themselves. Due to the existence of massive information, and Sealincloud platform cannot eliminate possible risks and defects. You should carefully judge and determine the authenticity, legality and validity of the relevant information, and pay attention to retaining relevant evidence for rights protection.</p>
            <p class="content">7.1.3  Users should comply with national laws, regulations and policy provisions in the process of using Sealincloud services, and the consequences arising from their use of Sealincloud services shall be borne by the users themselves.</p>
            <p class="">7.2</p>
            <p class="content">The information posted by users through the Sealincloud service and any opinions transmitted through the Sealincloud service do not represent the position of Sealincloud, and Sealincloud is not responsible for their completeness, truthfulness, accuracy or reliability. Users should make their own judgments on illegal, unethical, wrong or other inappropriate information that may be encountered on Sealincloud, and content that is misclassified or deceptive. In any case, any loss or damage caused by the aforementioned improper information should be borne by the relevant behavior subject.</p>
            <p class="">7.3</p>
            <p class="content">Given that the content of the web page pointed to by the external link is not actually controlled by the operator of Sealincloud, the operator of Sealincloud cannot guarantee the accuracy and completeness of the external link set for the convenience of users.</p>
            <p class="">7.4</p>
            <p class="content">For the interruption or other defects of the Sealincloud service caused by force majeure or reasons beyond the control of the operator of Sealincloud, the operator of Sealincloud does not assume any responsibility, but will try to reduce the loss and impact on users. After the force majeure event is eliminated, the operator of Sealincloud should immediately resume the provision of services.</p>
            <p class="">7.5</p>
            <p class="content">7.5.1You agree, and ensure that when you find that any content of this website does not comply with legal regulations, or does not comply with the provisions of this user agreement, you have the obligation to notify Sealincloud in a timely manner. If you find that your personal information has been stolen, your copyright or other rights have been infringed, please inform Sealincloud of this situation and at the same time provide the following information and materials:</p>
            <p class="content">
              a. The URL, number or other details that can find the information that infringes your rights;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b. The proof of your legal ownership of the copyright or other rights mentioned;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c. Your contact information, including the name of the contact person, address, phone number, and email;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;d. Your ID card photocopy, business license and other relevant materials.
            Upon verification, we will delete the relevant information in time. We only accept written infringement notices by mail, email or fax. In urgent situations, you can notify us through the customer service phone, and we will take appropriate measures depending on the situation.
            <br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The "appropriate measures" referred to in 7.5.1 of this agreement include but are not limited to one or more of the following:<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a.  Change, delete or block relevant content;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b.  Warning of violation account, account mute;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c.  Change, restrict or prohibit some or all functions of the violation account;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;d.  Suspend, restrict or terminate the user's right to use Sealincloud services, cancel the user account, etc.;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.  Report to the relevant regulatory authorities or state agencies;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;f.  Other measures that the operator of Sealincloud considers reasonable.<br/>
            </p>
            <p class="">7.6</p>
            <p class="content">Sealincloud does not assume responsibility for losses caused by force majeure. The force majeure referred to in this service clause includes: natural disasters, changes in laws, regulations or government orders, unique reasons for network services, such as failures of domestic and foreign basic telecommunications operators, computer or Internet-related technical defects, limitations of Internet coverage, computer viruses, hacker attacks and other factors, and other objective situations within the legal scope that cannot be foreseen, avoided and overcome.</p>
            <p class="">7.7</p>
            <p class="content">The operator of Sealincloud shall bear the relevant responsibilities for the Sealincloud services provided to users in accordance with the law, unless otherwise provided by law or agreed.</p>
            <p class="title1">8.  User Management</p>
            <p class="">8.1</p>
            <p class="content"> Users are solely responsible for the content they publish. Users must comply with all local, national, and international laws applicable to the service. Users promise:</p>
            <p class="content">8.1.1  When users post information on Sealincloud's web pages or related software applications, or use Sealincloud's services, they must comply with Chinese regulations. They may not create, copy, publish, or disseminate the following types of information on Sealincloud's web pages, related software applications, or using Sealincloud's services:</p>
            <p class="content">
              a. Violating the basic principles established by the constitution;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b. Endangering national security, leaking state secrets, subverting state power, and undermining national unity;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c. Damaging national honor and interests;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;d. Inciting ethnic hatred or discrimination, and undermining ethnic unity;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e. Undermining national religious policies and promoting cults and feudal superstitions;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;f. Spreading rumors, disrupting social order, and undermining social stability;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;g. Spreading obscenity, pornography, gambling, violence, terror, or inciting crimes;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;h. Insulting or slandering others, infringing upon the legal rights and interests of others;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i. Inciting illegal assemblies, associations, marches, demonstrations, and mass disturbances of social order;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j. Conducting activities in the name of illegal civil organizations;<br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k. Containing other content prohibited by laws and administrative regulations.<br/>

            </p>
            <p class="">8.2</p>
            <p class="content">When users post information on Sealincloud's web pages or use Sealincloud's services, they must also comply with other relevant national and regional laws and regulations, as well as relevant international laws. Users must use Sealincloud's services in accordance with legal regulations.</p>
            <p class="">8.3</p>
            <p class="content">Users may not use Sealincloud's services to engage in the following activities:<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a.  Unauthorized access to computer information networks or use of computer information network resources;<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b.  Unauthorized deletion, modification, or addition to the functions of computer information networks;<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c.  Unauthorized deletion, modification, or addition to data and applications stored, processed, or transmitted in computer information networks;<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;d.  Deliberate creation and dissemination of destructive programs such as computer viruses;<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.  Other behaviors that endanger computer information network security.<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;f.  Users may not interfere with Sealincloud's services in any way.<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;g.  Users may not abuse Sealincloud's services, including but not limited to: using Sealincloud's services to infringe upon the intellectual property rights or other legal interests of others.<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;h.  Users must comply with all other provisions and procedures of Sealincloud.<br/>
            </p>
            <p class="">8.4</p>
            <p class="content">Users must bear legal responsibility for their actions during the use of Sealincloud's services. The forms of legal responsibility borne by users include, but are not limited to:
            Compensating the infringed party, and when Sealincloud first assumes the administrative penalty or infringement damage compensation liability caused by the user's behavior, the user should provide Sealincloud with an equivalent compensation. If the user violates the above provisions, Sealincloud has the right to make an independent judgment and immediately suspend or terminate the provision of all or part of the services to the user, including freezing or canceling the user's service account and other measures.
            Users understand that if Sealincloud finds that the information transmitted by its website obviously belongs to one of the contents listed in paragraph 8.1, according to Chinese law, Sealincloud is obliged to immediately stop transmission, save related records, report to the relevant national authorities, and delete the address, directory containing that content, or shut down the server.
            <br/>
            </p>
            <p class="">8.5</p>
            <p class="content">In addition to the user management provisions in 8.1, 8.2, 8.3, and 8.4, media users should note:</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.1  Media customers may not submit forged identity documents to obtain journalist status for illegal activities. If the account registration information provided by the user to Sealincloud is inaccurate, untrue, contains illegal or bad information, Sealincloud has the right not to register, and reserves the right to terminate the user's use of various Sealincloud services. If the user deceives the account registration with false information or the account avatar, personal profile, and other registration information contain illegal and bad information, Sealincloud has the right to take measures such as notifying correction within a time limit, suspending use, and canceling registration.</p>
            <p class="">8.5.2</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.2.1  Real-name certified journalists may not engage in news trading for profit, and users may not use Sealincloud's services for sales or other commercial purposes.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.2.2  Real-name certified journalists may not extort money from the parties involved in the news.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.2.3  Real-name certified journalists may not ask for benefits from whistleblowers.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.3  Media users may not use the leaked information for false publication, tampering with facts, fabricating facts, maliciously slander others. They must ensure that the relevant information published and disseminated is true, valid, and legal, and guarantee to bear and compensate Sealincloud for any losses caused to Sealincloud based on the information published by them, including but not limited to the losses and damage to reputation and goodwill caused to Sealincloud due to compensation to the complained party or users.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.4   If the citizen does not hide the phone number, or informs the real-name certified journalist of his personal identity information, without the consent of others, he may not disclose others' privacy, such as others' names, portraits, addresses, phone numbers, financial status, family life, physiological defects, medical history, past experiences, and other private information that should not be publicly shown to people.</p>
            <p class="">8.5.5</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.5.1  Interviews involving privacy should preferably be conducted with the consent of the interviewee. And request them to sign on the interview book or record the interviewee's consent to broadcast through the camera.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.5.2  For interviewees other than whistleblowers, informers, and those who actively request interviews, if sensitive privacy is involved, necessary technical processing should be done on their faces and pseudonyms should be used; materials that infringe on others' privacy should not be used for further dissemination.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.6  Reporting on criminal cases in the investigation stage needs to be cautious. In principle, only information on the progress of the case can be made public, and detailed investigation information is not disclosed. The report should revolve around the report manuscripts or speeches of the investigation organs, and no arbitrary extension is allowed. In comments, it should be noted that there should be no presumption of guilt for the suspect, and the report should not be biased;</p>
            <p class="content">For news materials provided by public security organs and judicial organs, a reasonable review should be conducted. Once a report that damages others' reputation rights occurs, a corrective report should be made in a timely manner. Media users need to handle it carefully and feedback to the platform in time for timely and proper handling.</p>
            <p class="content">8.5.7  Media users should comply with this agreement, "Media News Infringement Legal Risk Warning", "Sealincloud Privacy Policy" and other related regulations. Sealincloud service platform has fulfilled its obligation to inform, and media users shall bear the consequences of violating the above regulations.</p>
            <p class="">8.6</p>
            <p class="content">In addition to the user management provisions in 8.1, 8.2, 8.3, and 8.4, citizen users should note:</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.1  Citizen users may not provide false leaks, fabricate facts, and maliciously slander others. They need to ensure that the statements and materials provided are true, valid, and legal, and guarantee to bear and compensate Sealincloud for any losses caused to Sealincloud based on the materials provided by them, including but not limited to the losses and damage to reputation and goodwill caused to Sealincloud due to compensation to the complained party or users.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.2  Ensure that their leaked works do not contain content that violates the constitution, laws, and harms public interest.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.3  Respect objective facts and not maliciously seek media for guided reporting through news trading and other means.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.4  Citizen users are responsible for any infringement of others' privacy rights, portrait rights, copyright, etc. in the content or uploaded pictures of the leaks, and Sealincloud is not responsible for this. If the content of the photo needs to be blocked, please process it in advance before uploading it to this platform.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.5  If the real-name certified journalist provides contact information to the citizen, without the consent of others, he may not disclose others' privacy, such as others' names, portraits, addresses, phone numbers, financial status, family life, physiological defects, medical history, past experiences, and other private information that should not be publicly shown to people.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.6  The way citizen users grant us, media users, and third parties the right to use the published information includes but is not limited to: disseminating to the public through the internet, copying, excerpting, performing, playing, exhibiting, distributing, filming movies, TV, video products, recording audio products, making digital products, adapting, translating, annotating, editing, and publishing, licensing other media, websites, and units to reprint, excerpt, play, record, translate, annotate, edit, adapt, film.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.7  For issues involving government public officials' discipline, please feedback to the official disciplinary inspection and supervision department, this platform will not publish.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.8  In principle, only the progress of criminal cases can be made public. If the content of the disclosure does not inform this platform of the confidential content of the criminal case, the consequences of the behavior shall be borne by the citizen user.</p>
            <p class="content">8.6.9  Citizen users should comply with this agreement, "Media News Infringement Legal Risk Tips", "Sealincloud Privacy Policy" and other related regulations. Sealincloud service platform has fulfilled its obligation to inform, and the citizen user shall bear the consequences of violating the above regulations. Note: If users have any questions about this agreement, they can contact Sealincloud customer service for consultation at any time.</p>
            <p class="title1">9.  Agreement Modification</p>
            <p class="">9.1</p>
            <p class="content">The operator of Sealincloud reserves the right to modify any terms of this agreement at any time. Once the content of this agreement changes, the operator of Sealincloud will publish the modified agreement content on the Sealincloud platform, ... the operator can also choose to notify users of the modified content through other appropriate ways (such as system notifications).</p>
            <p class="">9.2</p>
            <p class="content">If you do not agree with the modifications made by the operator of Sealincloud to the terms of this agreement, you have the right to stop using Sealincloud services. If you continue to use Sealincloud services, it is considered that you accept the modifications made by the operator of Sealincloud to the terms of this agreement.</p>
            <p class="title1">10. Notice Delivery</p>
            <p class="">10.1</p>
            <p class="content">All notices from the operator of Sealincloud to users under this agreement can be delivered through webpage announcements, emails, system notifications, proactive contacts from Sealincloud management accounts, private messages, mobile text messages, or regular mail; such notices are deemed to have been delivered to the recipient on the day of sending. Users should respond within three working days after receiving the notice.</p>
            <p class="">10.2</p>
            <p class="content">User's notice to the operator of Sealincloud should be delivered through the officially announced contact information of the operator of Sealincloud, such as communication address, fax number, email address, etc. And, any notice sent by the user is considered delivered only after the operator of Sealincloud confirms receipt.</p>
            <p class="title1">11. Applicable Law</p>
            <p class="">11.1</p>
            <p class="content">The conclusion, execution, interpretation and dispute resolution of this agreement shall be governed by the laws of the mainland of the People's Republic of China. This agreement is governed by the laws of the People's Republic of China. Both parties agree that in the process of interpreting and applying this agreement, they should follow the laws and judicial interpretations of the People's Republic of China.</p>
            <p class="">11.2</p>
            <p class="content">In case of any dispute between the two parties over the content or execution of this agreement, the two parties should try to resolve it through friendly negotiation; if the negotiation fails, the user must file a lawsuit in the Futian District Court of Shenzhen, where the operator of Sealincloud is located.</p>
            <p class="title1">12. Other Provisions</p>
            <p class="">12.1</p>
            <p class="content"> If any provision of this agreement is wholly or partially invalid or unenforceable for any reason, the remaining provisions of this agreement shall remain valid and binding.</p>
            <p class="">12.2</p>
            <p class="content"> The titles in this agreement are set for convenience only and should be ignored in interpreting this agreement and cannot be used as the basis for interpreting the terms of this agreement. Sealincloud operator reserves the right at any time, for any reason, without notice, to modify, suspend, terminate or interrupt all or part of the Sealincloud service.</p>
